"============================================
"üì± RESPONSIVE DESIGN - DISE√ëO ADAPTABLE
"============================================
"Aprende a crear p√°ginas que se adaptan a cualquier tama√±o de pantalla.

"¬øQU√â ES RESPONSIVE DESIGN?
"----------------------------------------
'Dise√±o que se adapta autom√°ticamente al dispositivo
'Misma p√°gina funciona en: m√≥vil, tablet, desktop
'Usa: media queries, flexbox, grid, unidades relativas

"MEDIA QUERIES
"----------------------------------------
'@media (max-width: 768px) { } - M√≥viles
'@media (min-width: 769px) { } - Tablets y desktop
'@media (min-width: 1200px) { } - Desktop grande

"BREAKPOINTS COMUNES
"----------------------------------------
'320px - M√≥vil peque√±o
'480px - M√≥vil grande
'768px - Tablet
'1024px - Desktop peque√±o
'1200px+ - Desktop grande

"META VIEWPORT
"----------------------------------------
'<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
